         <abstract id="aspace_13bcbfeec3a27a7e7ef99c47228a45be">The papers consist of correspondence, writings, printed matter, photographs, and minutes and reports relating primarily to Theodore Badger's term on the board of directors of the International Grenfell Association.</abstract>
