      <scopecontent id="aspace_36d2de1ff0fc5fead2a44b7a8efb45cf">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Theodore L. Badger Papers contain material documenting Dr. Badger's affiliation with the International Grenfell Association (I.G.A.). Theodore Badger, colleague and friend of Sir Wilfred Grenfell, served on the Board of Directors of the I.G.A. from 1948-1975 and was chairman from 1952-1953. The papers consist of correspondence, writings, printed matter, photographs, and I.G.A. minutes and reports. Dr. Badger's correspondence with Sir Wilfred and Lady Ann Grenfell is of particular interest.</p>
         <p>The Theodore L. Badger Papers were donated to Yale University by Mrs. Badger in 1984.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
